Package: trainr
Type: Package
Title: Learn R by Trial and Error (TDD)
Version: 0.4.1
Author: Eric Burden
Maintainer: Eric Burden <eric@ericburden.dev>
Description: Inspired by numerous exercises, including notably the Ruby Koans,
    this package aims to help R learners develop a solid foundation in R using
    the Red > Green > Refactor approach of Test-Driven Development (TDD).
